; Compute 5! = 120 using recursion.
; MEM[0] is a shared scratch cell: after each recursive CALL returns, the frame
; stores its partial product there (STORE 0) before restoring its saved n (POP).
; 11 cells is the smallest stack that safely fits the full call tree for n = 5.
.memory 11

LOADI 5
CALL fact
HALT

fact:
JZ fact_base
PUSH
SUB 1
CALL fact
STORE 0
POP
MULM 0
RET

fact_base:
LOADI 1
RET
